citation: Proclamation under the Credit (Commonwealth Powers) Act 2009 (Tas)
text:
Proclamation under the Credit (Commonwealth Powers) Act 2009

I, the Governor in and over the State of Tasmania and its Dependencies in the Commonwealth of Australia, acting with the advice of the Executive Council, by this my proclamation made under section 2 of the Credit (Commonwealth Powers) Act 2009 fix 17 November 2009 as the day on which that Act commences.

16 November 2009

PETER G. UNDERWOOD

Governor

By His Excellency's Command,

L. E. THORP

Minister for Human Services acting for and on behalf of the Minister for Corrections and Consumer Protection

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 17 November 2009

This proclamation is administered in the Department of Justice.
